.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH dkp-search 1  "search 0.1.0" 
.SH NAME
dkp\-search \- Full\-text BM25 search across machine assets (or registry with \-\-registry)
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdkp search\fR [\fB\-\-output\fR] [\fB\-\-registry\fR] [\fB\-q\fR|\fB\-\-quiet\fR] [\fB\-\-type\fR] [\fB\-\-limit\fR] [\fB\-v\fR|\fB\-\-verbose\fR] [\fB\-\-audience\fR] [\fB\-\-domain\fR] [\fB\-\-conformance\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fB\-V\fR|\fB\-\-version\fR] [\fIPACK\fR] [\fIQUERY\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Full\-text BM25 search across machine assets (or registry with \-\-registry)
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-output\fR \fI<OUTPUT>\fR [default: plain]
Output format
.br

.br
\fIPossible values:\fR
.RS 14
.IP \(bu 2
plain: Human\-readable plain text (default)
.IP \(bu 2
table: Aligned table using comfy\-table
.IP \(bu 2
json: Pretty\-printed JSON
.RE
.TP
\fB\-\-registry\fR
Search the registry index instead of a local pack
.TP
\fB\-q\fR, \fB\-\-quiet\fR
Suppress informational output; print only results
.TP
\fB\-\-type\fR \fI<TYPE>\fR
Narrow results to a specific asset type
.TP
\fB\-\-limit\fR \fI<LIMIT>\fR [default: 10]
Maximum number of results
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
Print debug info (schema paths, provider calls, etc.)
.TP
\fB\-\-audience\fR \fI<ID>\fR
Filter content to assets tagged for a specific audience profile
.TP
\fB\-\-domain\fR \fI<NAME>\fR

.TP
\fB\-\-conformance\fR \fI<LEVEL>\fR

.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.TP
\fB\-V\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
Print version
.TP
[\fIPACK\fR]
Path to the DKP bundle (omit when using \-\-registry)
.TP
[\fIQUERY\fR]
Search query
.SH VERSION
v0.1.0
